<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空瞪着那两个害怕的和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“袈裟不见了？”他大叫，“袈裟到底去哪儿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不知道！”一个和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们试着去找过。”另一个和尚补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那袈裟原本在一个一点儿都没被烧到的屋子里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但现在它不在那里了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空立刻从耳朵里掏出金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“长！”悟空命令道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挥着金箍棒朝两个和尚打去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的金箍棒还没有碰到那两个和尚，悟空就把它扔掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空倒在地上，痛苦地大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好疼啊！好疼啊！”他大叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧默默地念着紧箍咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空四下打滚，又踢又叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个和尚跳起来向后退。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要再念咒了！”悟空朝着唐僧大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我求求你！我不会伤害那些和尚了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧停止了念咒，悟空站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空做了一次深呼吸，然后把金箍棒放进了耳朵里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧看着那两个和尚：“你们真的不知道袈裟在哪儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的不知道。”一个和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“住持昨晚逃走了。他没带着袈裟一起走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摸了摸下巴：“可能是被妖怪偷走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这附近有什么妖魔鬼怪吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人觉得附近的山上有妖怪。”另一个和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们说那是个黑熊精。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去看看是不是那只熊拿走了袈裟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空说，“我去去就来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跃上空中飞了一阵，落在了山里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走了一会儿，听到了说话的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他藏在一块巨石后面悄悄地看着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>结果看到了一群妖怪在说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其中，有一只很大的黑熊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那只熊大声笑着：“那寺院昨晚着火了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我下山去查看，结果发现了一件极好的袈裟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得这是佛祖的宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不管怎样，我把它偷来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今晚，我要举行宴会，好好儿庆祝一下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当悟空听到其他妖怪笑起来时，非常愤怒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跃过了巨石，落在了那群妖怪中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“立刻把袈裟还给我！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抽出了金箍棒：“不然，我就打死你们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪们四处逃窜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空追在黑熊精身后，直至一个洞口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑熊跑进了洞里，猛地关上门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大力捶打着岩洞的大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“立刻给我出来，不然我就砸了这门！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞门打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑熊精走了出来。他拿着长矛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么敢捶我的门，还对我大叫！”他高声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你偷了我师父的袈裟！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想干吗，就干吗。”黑熊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是黑风王。我是这山里最有本事的妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是孙悟空，花果山大王。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我五百年前大闹天宫，玉帝的天兵天将都不能打败我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑风王哼了一声：“我没听说过。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用长矛向悟空捅过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐当！悟空用他的金箍棒挡住了长矛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这二人打斗时，山上的石头都震动了起来，纷纷滚下山去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>斗了一个小时后，黑风王举起了一只手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要休息一下。我得吃午饭了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空张大了嘴巴：“你说什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空还没来得及说话，黑熊精转身跑进了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门又被关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>